---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---
<section class="hero-bg relative min-h-[80vh] md:min-h-[90vh] flex items-center justify-center text-white" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60 z-0"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p 
        class="text-yellow-400 font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm md:text-base animate-fade-in"
        style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
        Complejo Deportivo y Recreativo
      </p>
      <h1
        id="hero-heading"
        class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold my-4 text-shadow-md animate-slide-in-down"
        style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
        Tu Pasión por el Fútbol Vive Aquí
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-base md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed text-gray-200 animate-slide-in-up"
        style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
        Las mejores canchas de césped natural en la Sabana de Bogotá. Entrena, compite y celebra en un ambiente profesional y familiar.
      </p>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 animate-zoom-in"
        style="animation-delay: 0.7s;">
        <a
          href="#contacto"
          class="w-full sm:w-auto bg-yellow-500 text-gray-900 font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full hover:bg-yellow-400 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg"
          aria-label="Reservar una cancha en ProFútbol JC">
          Reservar Cancha
        </a>
        <a
          href="#torneos"
          class="w-full sm:w-auto bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-gray-900 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105"
          aria-label="Ver los próximos torneos de fútbol">
          Ver Torneos
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-bg {
  
    background-image: url('/images/header.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-attachment: fixed; 
  }

  .text-shadow-md {
    text-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }


  @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }
  @keyframes slideInDown { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  @keyframes slideInUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  @keyframes zoomIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.9); } to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); } }

  .animate-fade-in { animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out forwards; }
  .animate-slide-in-down { animation: slideInDown 0.8s ease-out forwards; }
  .animate-slide-in-up { animation: slideInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards; }
  .animate-zoom-in { animation: zoomIn 0.8s ease-out forwards; }
</style>